column1: #   This data summarizes the fold-change in gene expression of this work overall
#   biological replicates. Note that this data is ONLY used for plotting
#   purposes and should not be used for any inference
#   IPTGuM: IPTG concentration in units of micromolar
#   class: Identifier for the class of mutation
#          DNA -> Mutation in DNA binding domain
#          IND -> Mutation in the inducer binding domain
#          DBL -> Double mutation (one in DNA binding domain
#   operator: Identifier of the operator sequence
#   repressors: Mean number of repressors per cell
#   mean: Mean fold-change over all biological replicates
#   sem: Standard error of the mean for all biological replicates
